{"tid":1955371,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] 崩壞3rd [7] 新職女武神．榮光出啦！武漢肺炎完一定都仲未1001","createTime":"2020-04-02T12:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T16:56:36.000Z","uid":37890,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c24162c0c64acd8d46880881eb09009e0406cbf9","tid":1955371,"uid":37890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:08:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://uploadstatic-sea.mihoyo.com/contentweb/20200402/2020040210410315886.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuploadstatic-sea.mihoyo.com%2Fcontentweb%2F20200402%2F2020040210410315886.png&h=a67408c0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《崩壞 3rd》是一款由上海團隊米哈遊（miHoYo）在 iOS 與 Android 雙平台上推出的動作角色扮演遊戲，同時也是《崩壞學園》系列的最新作。本作講述了琪亞娜一行人加入 「 女武神部隊 」 後對抗 「 崩壞 」的故事，玩家將透過操縱性格各異的女武神，與出沒於世界各處的死士、崩壞獸戰鬥，挑戰崩壞帶來的絕望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=THKDkZ70SIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTHKDkZ70SIo&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=fb915278\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=THKDkZ70SIo</a><br />\n<br />\n- 下載台服 -<br />\nIOS：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/ct6qA4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fct6qA4&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=8bc1e91a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ct6qA4</a><br />\nAN：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/sgFujL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsgFujL&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=f62f8581\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/sgFujL</a><br />\n電腦版：<a href=\"https://honkaiimpact3.mihoyo.com/tw/zh-tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhonkaiimpact3.mihoyo.com%2Ftw%2Fzh-tw&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=8148cc70\" target=\"_blank\">https://honkaiimpact3.mihoyo.com/tw/zh-tw</a><br />\n<br />\n- 3.8版本宣傳片-<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mi0fsClgnOo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fmi0fsClgnOo&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=6c3041fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mi0fsClgnOo</a><br />\n<br />\n初始A角 - 女武神．榮光<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCkFZ39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCkFZ39.jpg&h=abc8da3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(下版)3.9版本</span></strong></span>初始S角 - 輝騎士．月魄<br />\n <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pRcKQvY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpRcKQvY.gif&h=45cfc028&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EStdJEx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEStdJEx.gif&h=27e6a8d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1nzzzQL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1nzzzQL.gif&h=1999e9c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XT7RV6B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXT7RV6B.gif&h=ec4ed725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\nＱ：幾時先叫做首抽？<br />\nＡ：打到1-5，抽完緋紅後，自己再用水晶抽嘅就係首抽。新手嘅頭四抽內必定會出一隻非御三家角色。抽到角色之後就會變返做十抽保底機制。2.3版本新增首33抽標準補給會保底一隻S角。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：使唔使儲夠石嚟十連抽？<br />\nＡ：唔使，因為單抽同十連抽一樣有保底機制，即係你分開嚟單抽十次同十連抽係完全冇分別嘅。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：首抽刷咩好？<br />\nＡ：由於所有A角都可以好快刷出嚟，有時間建議刷初始S角起手(33抽標準內必出)<br />\n刷首抽S建議： 神恩&gt;月輪(台服就出)&gt;玫瑰&gt;次元&gt;熾翎&gt;鬼鎧&gt;月光&gt;紫苑<br />\n御三家S(月光/鬼鎧/次元)隻隻都勁，但由於可以用6000石選其中一隻(只限一次)，所以優先度唔高<br />\n<br />\nＱ：初始S角係咪一定好過A角？<br />\nＡ：呢隻game角色評價主要睇兩方面：戰場同埋深淵<br />\n1：戰場基本上係大佬爭排名先用，講求齊角齊裝，平民玩家拎低保分既唔需要初S角<br />\n2：深淵係呢個遊戲水晶主要收入(佔差唔多一半)，主流隊伍都係靠神恩同次元呢兩隻神sup，地位有如FGO既梅孔一樣，但如果冇呢兩隻，靠初A角打都打到，但拎少D石<br />\n<br />\n*所有非初始S角色嘅碎片都可以靠刷關卡嚟獲得，升級上SSS。而初始S角嘅碎片大部分要抽返黎，少部分有得刷都要好長時間。除非重課，如果唔係都幾難升上SS，SSS。所以自行斟酌啦。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：新手時期點玩上去好？<br />\nＡ：加個師傅先，再全力推主線，中期刷碎片最為重要。星期一至五曜日可以唔打，會送返徽章比你可以週末自選關卡開，星期六日金幣關必清，無打唔會回徽章。活動關做到3個成就可以清，另外唔夠打/死左角色可以直接退出，呢隻game係通關結算先扣體力。<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點樣升艦長lv最快？<br />\nＡ：因為1體力=1經驗，所以唔會有話打邊關升得特別快。最快嘅方法就係一路衝主線，可以攞主線任務經驗。<br />\n(50lv前新手有送經驗加倍，自己入裝備果格到開)<br />\n<br />\nＱ：啲水晶點樣用最好？<br />\nＡ：每日買兩次體力。<del>歐洲人可以選擇all in抽補給</del><br />\n25鑽=60體 每日建議買2次<br />\n10鑽=2萬幾 發覺唔夠錢用既都可以買(唔建議)<br />\n新手期標準抽左隻初S先，再主力抽裝備(精準補給)<br />\n課長就乜鳩都抽啦<br />\n<br />\nQ：台/日/陸服點揀好？<br />\n台：大部分巴打都玩台服，版本都追上左日服，只落後陸服1個版本，可以選用中/日語音<br />\n日：少量巴打玩，抽補給冇十抽補底，但過關石頭送多過台服(唔係多好多)，歐洲人岩玩<br />\n陸：原廠版本，乜都最新，實體福利最多(比如全服滿級既每人派一箱薯片)但最多bugs同屎食，課金比較麻煩，但人最多，多到以十萬到百萬計<br />\n<br />\nQ：唔課會唔會玩唔落去<br />\nA：唔追排名既0課都玩到，唔少平民戰神都幾揪得，但建議每個月課月卡($38蚊拎到$200既石)<br />\n而呢隻驚好考技術操作，就算課左金<del>課得唔夠</del>，技術唔夠都冇用<br />\n<br />\nQ：有冇連登仔艦團？會唔會冇位？<br />\nA：有意入團既，申請左之後係度留game名，或者入TG谷搵正副團長<br />\n艦團名：LIHKG<br />\n編號:1000013<br />\n位呢家野，擠一擠還是有的<br />\n<br />\nQ：點解個post推唔郁？是咪冇人玩？<br />\nA：<del>成也TG谷，敗也TG谷。基本上TG谷每日都1000條msg+ 最多時3000+都有，無錯，講緊你班友唔黎推post。<br />\n台服最近玩既人數都上升緊</del><br />\n是<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NeI9z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNeI9z.jpg&h=91695041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實用連結：<br />\n【心得】隊伍組成簡明指南及角色定位簡評（巴哈）：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/c138cS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fc138cS&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=a6c5c839\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/c138cS</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【心得】3.3版本適用の新手攻略！</span></strong>：<a href=\"http://shorturl.at/diCEX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshorturl.at%2FdiCEX&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=2dd92f59\" target=\"_blank\">shorturl.at/diCEX</a><br />\n<strong>老鹹魚的崩壞3 wiki</strong>：<a href=\"https://bh3momeha.game-info.wiki/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbh3momeha.game-info.wiki%2F&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=57e210c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://bh3momeha.game-info.wiki/</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新手注意勿賣暈槍！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NfQIN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNfQIN.jpg&h=cdd6690e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">老婆鎮樓❗️<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pximg.net/img-master/img/2019/05/02/15/57/51/73572009_p0_master1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pximg.net%2Fimg-master%2Fimg%2F2019%2F05%2F02%2F15%2F57%2F51%2F73572009_p0_master1200.jpg&h=6afc4a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫師淺春pixiv ： <a href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/artworks/73572009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fartworks%2F73572009&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=7c39d390\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pixiv.net/artworks/73572009</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b1ca4d5913a524a6dfbc9af4de467ba8dae4c9","tid":1955371,"uid":37890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"肺炎完之前爆到post想我點都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf80232d54ed273d93e7dedcc33bb44176369ae","tid":1955371,"uid":276101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2ae06e22a0d99aff443154ed13e18d0cce04fae1","tid":1955371,"uid":22387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4b1ca4d5913a524a6dfbc9af4de467ba8dae4c9","tid":1955371,"uid":37890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"肺炎完之前爆到post想我點都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"找左舊數未？"},{"pid":"f984959ee0af9df9317c97bd14037fc76a3df931","tid":1955371,"uid":204771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ae06e22a0d99aff443154ed13e18d0cce04fae1","tid":195537